    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="什么是hexo">什么是hexo</h2>
<blockquote>
<p>A fast, simple &amp; powerful blog framework, powered by Node.js.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>hexo是一个基于Node.js的静态博客程序，可以方便的生成静态网页托管在github上。<br>以下简单介绍hexo搭建博客的过程</p>
<a id="more"></a>

<h2 id="Linux_ubuntu">Linux ubuntu</h2>
<p>install git<br>install node.js<br><em>每次</em>nvm use 0.10.35(node.js版本号)<br>npm install -g hexo<br>cd到你的博客文件目录 hexo init初始化<br>npm install    //安装依赖包(public里文件是hexo要发布)</p>
<p>Enjoy writing blog!</p>
<h4 id="Hexo_常用命令"><strong>Hexo 常用命令</strong></h4>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">hexo new</div><div class="line">hexo generate</div><div class="line">hexo server</div><div class="line">hexo develop</div><div class="line">hexo clean</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

]]></content>
